headline: Welltower's Credit Rating Upgraded by S&P Global Ratings to 'A-' and by Moody's Investor Services to 'A3'
summary: Welltower Inc. (NYSE: WELL) (the "Company") today announced that S&P Global Ratings ("S&P") and Moody's Investor Service, Inc. ("Moody's") raised their credit ratings related to the Company to "A-" with a stable outlook and to "A3" with a stable outlook, respectively.

headline: Here's Why You Should Retain Welltower Stock in Your Portfolio
summary: WELL is well-poised to gain from an aging population and a rise in senior citizens' healthcare expenditures. However, high competition is a concern.
